## Endpoints

```
# Assets  [auth.jwt]
POST   /api/v1/workspaces/{workspace}/assets/upload-url              CreateAssetUploadUrlController
POST   /api/v1/workspaces/{workspace}/assets/{asset}/confirm         ConfirmAssetUploadController
GET    /api/v1/workspaces/{workspace}/assets                         ListAssetsController           offset
GET    /api/v1/workspaces/{workspace}/assets/{asset}                 ShowAssetController
PATCH  /api/v1/workspaces/{workspace}/assets/{asset}                 UpdateAssetController
DELETE /api/v1/workspaces/{workspace}/assets/{asset}                 TrashAssetController

# Referencias cruzadas
POST   /api/v1/workspaces/{workspace}/asset-references               CreateAssetReferenceController
DELETE /api/v1/workspaces/{workspace}/asset-references/{reference}   DeleteAssetReferenceController
```

